with the end of the nazi regime , the division of germany into allied - occupation zones and the separation of its territories east of the oder–neisse line , which were incorporated into poland and the soviet union , the state of prussia ceased to exist de facto in 1945.christopher clark , iron kingdom : the rise and downfall of prussia , 1600–1947 ( 2006 ) is the standard history .

